          "reviewBody": "The school is absolute trash the space students have to play football is genuinely comical the teachers are the worst part I can not name 1 teacher that I honestly do not dislike the toilets in the school campus are so bad that if I make it a point to never go to them and just pray I can hold it in for the entire school day. The classrooms are dirty and it's always hot to the point that u get used to the stench from a class of 20+ sweaty students the quality of water in the school is also questionable I know many people who don't fill their water at school because they (Allegedly) are filled with tap water also the fact that every student after a certain age has to stand infront of the sum on a hot sunny day in INDIA for atleast 20mins this happens daily... I feel if the school REALLY NEEDS TO have an assembly in the morning it should be once a week at MOST. Also the dogs in the school genuinely look unwell the dogs they keep in the campus don't look like they are treated properly..\n\nOn a positive note.. there's nothing to say here since the school doesn't have anything positive that every other school doesn't have (in my opinion)",
